# Warehousing, Moving, Dismantling, and Installation Services (NCR) [Tender #100023726]
## Notice Information

* **Title**: Warehousing, moving, dismantling and installation services (NCR) - 100023726
* **Reference Number**: cb-7455-86712428
* **Solicitation Number**: 100023726
* **Publication Date**: July 21, 2023
* **Tender Closing Date**: August 18, 2023, 2:00 PM Eastern Daylight Time (EDT)

## Technical Specifications

* **Objectives**: Procure services from a qualified vendor to provide warehousing, moving, dismantling, and installation services for Employment and Social Development Canada (ESDC) on an "as and when requested” basis.
* **Services**: Moving, dismantling, and installation of office equipment and furniture, and related goods/services.
* **Location**: National Capital Region (NCR)
* **Storage Space**: Dedicated warehouse space in the NCR

## Tender Process

* **Procurement Type**: Competitive - Open Bidding
* **Selection Criteria**: Highest Combined Rating of Technical Merit and Price
* **Trade Agreements**: Compliant with Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA), Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA), and other applicable trade agreements.

## Supporting Documents

* **Tender Notice**: [Canadabuys Link]
* **Request for Proposal (RFP)**: English - [Canadabuys Link], French - [Canadabuys Link]
* **Q&A Part 1**: [Canadabuys Link]
* **Q&A Part 2**: [Canadabuys Link]
* **Amendment #1**: Q&A Part 1
* **Amendment #2**: Q&A Part 2, Slip sheet

## Contact Information

* **Contracting Entity**: Employment and Social Development Canada (ESDC)
* **Contact Name**: Estelle Benoit & Karine Chamberland
* **Contact Email**: NC-SOLICITATIONS-GD@hrsdc-rhdcc.gc.ca
* **Contact Phone**: 1234
* **Contact Fax**: Not available

## Notes
The tender has expired. Interested vendors can contact the contracting entity for clarification and information.
